com.hazelcast.query.impl

Class QueryableEntry<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.query.impl.QueryableEntry<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Extractable, Map.Entry<K,V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CachedQueryEntry, QueryEntry

    public abstract class QueryableEntry<K,V>
extends Object
implements Extractable, Map.Entry<K,V>
    This abstract class contains methods related to Queryable Entry, which means searched an indexed by SQL query or predicate.

    If the object, which is used as the extraction target, is not of Data or Portable type the serializationService will not be touched at all.
